{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I'm going to show you how terrorism"},{"time":3000,"text":"actually interacts with our daily life."},{"time":6000,"text":"15 years ago I received a phone call from a friend."},{"time":10000,"text":"At the time he was looking after the rights of political prisoners"},{"time":13000,"text":"in Italian jails."},{"time":16000,"text":"He asked me if I wanted to interview the Red Brigades."},{"time":20000,"text":"Now, as many of you may remember,"},{"time":22000,"text":"the Red Brigades was a terrorist, Marxist organization"},{"time":26000,"text":"which was very active in Italy"},{"time":28000,"text":"from the 1960s until the mid-1980s."},{"time":32000,"text":"As part of their strategy"},{"time":34000,"text":"the Red Brigades never spoke with anybody, not even with their lawyers."},{"time":38000,"text":"They sat in silence through their trails,"},{"time":42000,"text":"waving occasionally at family and friends."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46000,"text":"In 1993 they declared the end of the armed struggle."},{"time":52000,"text":"And they drew a list of people with whom they would talk,"},{"time":54000,"text":"and tell their story."},{"time":56000,"text":"And I was one of those people."},{"time":59000,"text":"When I asked my friend why the Red Brigades want to talk to me,"},{"time":62000,"text":"he said that the female members of the organization"},{"time":66000,"text":"had actually supported my name."},{"time":69000,"text":"In particular, one person had put it forward."},{"time":72000,"text":"She was my childhood friend."},{"time":75000,"text":"She had joined the Red Brigades"},{"time":77000,"text":"and became a leader of the organization."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80000,"text":"Naturally, I didn't know that"},{"time":82000,"text":"until the day she was arrested."},{"time":84000,"text":"In fact, I read it in the newspaper."},{"time":88000,"text":"At the time of the phone call"},{"time":90000,"text":"I just had a baby,"},{"time":92000,"text":"I successfully completed a management buyout"},{"time":94000,"text":"to the company I was working with,"},{"time":97000,"text":"and the last thing I wanted to do was to go back home"},{"time":100000,"text":"and touring the high-security prisons."},{"time":103000,"text":"But this is exactly what I did"},{"time":106000,"text":"because I wanted to know"},{"time":108000,"text":"what had turned my best friend"},{"time":110000,"text":"into a terrorist,"},{"time":112000,"text":"and why she'd never tried to recruit me."},{"time":116000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":118000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":121000,"text":"So, this is exactly what I did."},{"time":126000,"text":"Now, I found the answer very quickly."},{"time":130000,"text":"I actually had failed"},{"time":132000,"text":"the psychological profiling of a terrorist."},{"time":135000,"text":"The center committee of the Red Brigades"},{"time":137000,"text":"had judged me too single-minded"},{"time":139000,"text":"and too opinionated to become a good terrorist."},{"time":143000,"text":"My friend, on the other hand, she was a good terrorist"},{"time":146000,"text":"because she was very good at following orders."},{"time":149000,"text":"She also embraced violence."},{"time":152000,"text":"Because she believed that the only way"},{"time":154000,"text":"to unblock what, at the time,"},{"time":157000,"text":"was known as a blocked democracy,"},{"time":159000,"text":"Italy, a country run by the same party for 35 years"},{"time":163000,"text":"was the arms struggle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167000,"text":"At the same time, while I was interviewing the Red Brigades,"},{"time":170000,"text":"I also discovered that their life was not ruled"},{"time":173000,"text":"by politics or ideology,"},{"time":176000,"text":"but actually was ruled by economics."},{"time":179000,"text":"They were constantly short of cash."},{"time":182000,"text":"They were constantly searching for cash."},{"time":185000,"text":"Now, contrary to what many people believe,"},{"time":187000,"text":"terrorism is actually a very expensive business."},{"time":191000,"text":"I'll give you an idea."},{"time":193000,"text":"In the 1970s, the turnover of the Red Brigades"},{"time":198000,"text":"on a yearly basis"},{"time":200000,"text":"was seven million dollars."},{"time":202000,"text":"This is roughly between 100"},{"time":204000,"text":"and 150 million, today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206000,"text":"Now, you know, if you live underground"},{"time":209000,"text":"it's really hard to produce this amount of money."},{"time":214000,"text":"But this also explains why, when I was interviewing the Red Brigades,"},{"time":218000,"text":"and then, later on, other arms organizations,"},{"time":221000,"text":"including members of al-Zarqawi group in the Middle East,"},{"time":226000,"text":"everybody was extremely reluctant"},{"time":229000,"text":"to talk about ideology, or politics."},{"time":232000,"text":"Because they had no idea."},{"time":234000,"text":"The political vision of a terrorist organization"},{"time":238000,"text":"is decided by the leadership,"},{"time":241000,"text":"which, generally, is never more than five to seven people."},{"time":244000,"text":"All the others do, day in and day out,"},{"time":247000,"text":"is search for money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249000,"text":"Once, for example, I was interviewing"},{"time":251000,"text":"this part-timer from the Red Brigades."},{"time":254000,"text":"It was a psychiatrist. He loved sailing."},{"time":256000,"text":"He was a really keen sailor. And he had this beautiful boat."},{"time":260000,"text":"And he told me that the best time of his life"},{"time":262000,"text":"was when he was a member of the Red Brigades"},{"time":265000,"text":"and he went sailing, every summer, back and forth"},{"time":267000,"text":"from Lebanon, where he would pick up"},{"time":269000,"text":"Soviet weapons from the PLO,"},{"time":271000,"text":"and then carry them all the way to Sardinia"},{"time":274000,"text":"where the other arms organization from Europe would go"},{"time":277000,"text":"and take their share of the arms."},{"time":280000,"text":"For that service the Red Brigades were actually paid a fee,"},{"time":284000,"text":"which went to fund their organization."}]},{"cues":[{"time":287000,"text":"So, because I am a trained economist"},{"time":290000,"text":"and I think in economic terms,"},{"time":292000,"text":"all of the sudden I thought,"},{"time":294000,"text":"maybe there is something here."},{"time":296000,"text":"Maybe there is a link, a commercial link,"},{"time":298000,"text":"between one organization and another one."},{"time":302000,"text":"But it was only when I interviewed"},{"time":305000,"text":"Mario Moretti, the head of the Red Brigades,"},{"time":309000,"text":"the man who kidnapped and killed Aldo Moro,"},{"time":312000,"text":"Italian former prime minister,"},{"time":315000,"text":"that I finally realized"},{"time":317000,"text":"that terrorism is actually business."},{"time":320000,"text":"I was having lunch with him"},{"time":322000,"text":"in a high-security prison in Italy."},{"time":324000,"text":"And as we were eating,"},{"time":327000,"text":"I had the distinct feeling"},{"time":329000,"text":"that I was back in the city of London,"},{"time":332000,"text":"having lunch with a fellow banker or an economist."},{"time":336000,"text":"This guy thought in the same way I did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340000,"text":"So, I decided that I wanted to investigate the economics of terrorism."},{"time":346000,"text":"Naturally, nobody wanted to fund my research."},{"time":350000,"text":"In fact, I think many people thought that I was a bit crazy."},{"time":352000,"text":"You know, that woman that goes around to foundations"},{"time":355000,"text":"asking for money, thinking about the economics of terrorism."},{"time":359000,"text":"So, in the end, I took a decision"},{"time":362000,"text":"that, in retrospect, did change my life."},{"time":365000,"text":"I sold my company,"},{"time":367000,"text":"and funded the research myself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370000,"text":"And what I discovered"},{"time":372000,"text":"is this parallel reality,"},{"time":374000,"text":"another international economic system,"},{"time":378000,"text":"which runs parallel to our own,"},{"time":381000,"text":"which has been created by arms organizations"},{"time":383000,"text":"since the end of World War II."},{"time":385000,"text":"And what is even more shocking"},{"time":387000,"text":"is that this system"},{"time":391000,"text":"has followed, step by step, the evolution"},{"time":394000,"text":"of our own system,"},{"time":396000,"text":"of our Western capitalism."},{"time":398000,"text":"And there are three main stages."},{"time":401000,"text":"The first one is the state sponsor of terrorism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404000,"text":"The second one is the privatization of terrorism."},{"time":407000,"text":"And the third, of course, is the globalization of terrorism."},{"time":411000,"text":"So, state sponsor of terrorism,"},{"time":414000,"text":"feature of the Cold War."},{"time":416000,"text":"This is when the two superpowers were fighting"},{"time":418000,"text":"a war by proxy,"},{"time":420000,"text":"along the periphery of the sphere of influence,"},{"time":423000,"text":"fully funding arms organizations."},{"time":426000,"text":"A mix of legal and illegal activities is used."},{"time":429000,"text":"So, the link between crime and terror"},{"time":432000,"text":"is established very early on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435000,"text":"And here is the best example,"},{"time":437000,"text":"the Contras in Nicaragua, created by the CIA,"},{"time":440000,"text":"legally funded by the U.S. Congress,"},{"time":443000,"text":"illegally funded by the Reagan administration"},{"time":446000,"text":"via covert operation, for example, the Iran-Contra Affair."},{"time":452000,"text":"Then comes the late 1970s, early '80s,"},{"time":455000,"text":"and some groups successfully carry out"},{"time":458000,"text":"the privatization of terrorism."},{"time":460000,"text":"So, they gain independence from the sponsor,"},{"time":463000,"text":"and start funding themselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467000,"text":"Now, again we see a mix of legal and illegal activities."},{"time":472000,"text":"So, Arafat used to get a percentage"},{"time":475000,"text":"of the smuggling of hashish"},{"time":478000,"text":"from Bekáa Valley, which is the valley between Lebanon and Syria."},{"time":482000,"text":"And the IRA, which control the private transportation system"},{"time":486000,"text":"in Northern Ireland, did exactly the same thing."},{"time":489000,"text":"So, every single time"},{"time":491000,"text":"that somebody got into a taxi in Belfast"},{"time":494000,"text":"without knowing, actually,"},{"time":496000,"text":"was funding the IRA."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499000,"text":"But the great change came, of course,"},{"time":501000,"text":"with globalization and deregulation."},{"time":504000,"text":"This is when arms organization were able to link up,"},{"time":507000,"text":"also financially, with each other."},{"time":509000,"text":"But above all, they started to do"},{"time":511000,"text":"serious business with the world of crime."},{"time":514000,"text":"And together they money-laundered"},{"time":516000,"text":"their dirty business through the same channel."},{"time":520000,"text":"This is when we see the birth of the transnational"},{"time":523000,"text":"arms organization Al Qaeda."},{"time":526000,"text":"This is an organization that can raise money across border."},{"time":529000,"text":"But also that is able to carry out attacks"},{"time":532000,"text":"in more than one country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535000,"text":"Now, deregulation also brought back"},{"time":538000,"text":"rogue economics."},{"time":540000,"text":"So what is rogue economics?"},{"time":542000,"text":"Rogue economics is a force which is constantly"},{"time":544000,"text":"lurking in the background of history."},{"time":548000,"text":"It comes back at times of great transformation,"},{"time":551000,"text":"globalization being one of those transformations."},{"time":554000,"text":"It is at this times in which"},{"time":557000,"text":"politics actually loses control of the economy,"},{"time":560000,"text":"and the economy becomes a rogue force"},{"time":563000,"text":"working against us."},{"time":565000,"text":"It has happened before in history."},{"time":566000,"text":"It has happened with the fall of the Roman Empire."},{"time":570000,"text":"It has happened with Industrial Revolution."},{"time":572000,"text":"And it actually happened again, with the fall of the Berlin wall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577000,"text":"Now, I calculated how big was this international"},{"time":582000,"text":"economic system composed by crime,"},{"time":584000,"text":"terror, and illegal economy,"},{"time":587000,"text":"before 9-11."},{"time":589000,"text":"And it is a staggering 1.5 trillion dollars."},{"time":594000,"text":"It is trillions, it's not billions."},{"time":596000,"text":"This is about twice the GDP of the United Kingdom,"},{"time":599000,"text":"soon will be more,"},{"time":601000,"text":"considering where this country is going."},{"time":603000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":606000,"text":"Now, until 9-11,"},{"time":608000,"text":"the bulk of all this money"},{"time":610000,"text":"flew into the U.S. economy"},{"time":612000,"text":"because the bulk of the money was denominated in U.S. dollars"},{"time":616000,"text":"and the money laundering was taking place"},{"time":619000,"text":"inside the United States."},{"time":621000,"text":"The entry point, of course, of most of this money"},{"time":624000,"text":"were the off-shore facilities."},{"time":626000,"text":"So, this was a vital injection of cash"},{"time":630000,"text":"into the U.S. economy."},{"time":633000,"text":"Now, when I went to look at the figures of the U.S. money supply,"},{"time":638000,"text":"the U.S. money supply is the amount"},{"time":640000,"text":"of dollars that the Federal Reserve"},{"time":643000,"text":"prints every year"},{"time":645000,"text":"in order to satisfy"},{"time":647000,"text":"the increase in the demand for dollars,"},{"time":650000,"text":"which, of course, reflects the growth"},{"time":652000,"text":"of the economy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":654000,"text":"So, when I went to look at those figures, I noted that since the late 1960s"},{"time":658000,"text":"a growing number of these dollars"},{"time":662000,"text":"was actually leaving the United States,"},{"time":664000,"text":"never to come back."},{"time":667000,"text":"These were money taken out"},{"time":669000,"text":"in suitcases or in containers, in cash of course."},{"time":673000,"text":"These were money taken out by criminals and money launderers."},{"time":676000,"text":"These were money taken out to fund"},{"time":679000,"text":"the growth of the terror,"},{"time":681000,"text":"illegal and criminal economy."},{"time":685000,"text":"So, you see, what is the relationship?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":689000,"text":"The United States actually is a country"},{"time":693000,"text":"that is the reserve currency of the world."},{"time":697000,"text":"What does it mean? That means that"},{"time":699000,"text":"it has a privilege that other countries do not have."},{"time":702000,"text":"It can borrow against the total amount of dollars"},{"time":706000,"text":"in circulation in the world."},{"time":708000,"text":"This privilege is called seigniorage."},{"time":711000,"text":"No other country can do that."},{"time":714000,"text":"All the other countries, for example the United Kingdom,"},{"time":716000,"text":"can borrow only against the amount of money"},{"time":720000,"text":"in circulation inside its own borders."}]},{"cues":[{"time":724000,"text":"So, here is the implication of the relationship"},{"time":726000,"text":"between the worlds of crime, terror, and illegal economy, and our economy."},{"time":731000,"text":"The U.S. in the 1990s"},{"time":734000,"text":"was borrowing against the growth"},{"time":736000,"text":"of the terror, illegal and criminal economy."},{"time":740000,"text":"This is how close we are with this world."},{"time":745000,"text":"Now, this situation changed, of course, after 9-11,"},{"time":747000,"text":"because George Bush launched the War on Terror."},{"time":750000,"text":"Part of the War on Terror"},{"time":752000,"text":"was the introduction of the Patriot Act."},{"time":755000,"text":"Now, many of you know that the Patriot Act"},{"time":757000,"text":"is a legislation that greatly reduces"},{"time":760000,"text":"the liberties of Americans in order to protect them"},{"time":763000,"text":"against terrorism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":765000,"text":"But there is a section of the Patriot Act"},{"time":767000,"text":"which refers specifically to finance."},{"time":769000,"text":"And it is, in fact, an anti-money-laundering legislation."},{"time":773000,"text":"What the Patriot Act did was"},{"time":775000,"text":"to prohibit U.S. bank,"},{"time":777000,"text":"and U.S.-registered foreign banks"},{"time":779000,"text":"from doing any businesses with off-shore facilities."},{"time":783000,"text":"It closed that door between the money laundering"},{"time":786000,"text":"in dollars, and the U.S. economy."},{"time":789000,"text":"It also gave the U.S. monetary authorities"},{"time":794000,"text":"the right to monitor any dollar transaction"},{"time":797000,"text":"taking place anywhere in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":801000,"text":"Now, you can imagine what was the reaction of the international"},{"time":803000,"text":"finance and banking."},{"time":805000,"text":"All the bankers said to their clients,"},{"time":808000,"text":"\"Get out of the dollars and go and invest somewhere else.\""},{"time":811000,"text":"Now, the Euro was a newly born currency"},{"time":814000,"text":"of great opportunity for business, and, of course, for investment."},{"time":818000,"text":"And this is what people did."},{"time":820000,"text":"Nobody wants the U.S. monetary authority"},{"time":822000,"text":"to check their relationship,"},{"time":824000,"text":"to monitor their relationship with their clientele."},{"time":828000,"text":"The same thing happened, of course,"},{"time":830000,"text":"in the world of crime and terror."},{"time":834000,"text":"People simply moved their money-laundering activities"},{"time":839000,"text":"away from the United States"},{"time":842000,"text":"into Europe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":845000,"text":"Why did this happen? This happened because"},{"time":847000,"text":"the Patriot Act was a unilateral legislation."},{"time":850000,"text":"It was introduced only in the United States."},{"time":852000,"text":"And it was introduced only for the U.S. dollars."},{"time":855000,"text":"In Europe, a similar legislation"},{"time":857000,"text":"was not introduced."},{"time":859000,"text":"So, within six months"},{"time":861000,"text":"Europe became the epicenter"},{"time":863000,"text":"of the money-laundering activities"},{"time":866000,"text":"of the world."},{"time":869000,"text":"So, this is how incredible are the relationship"},{"time":873000,"text":"between the world of crime"},{"time":875000,"text":"and the world of terror,"},{"time":877000,"text":"and our own life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":880000,"text":"So, why did I tell you this story?"},{"time":882000,"text":"I told you this story because you"},{"time":884000,"text":"must understand that there is a world"},{"time":887000,"text":"that goes well beyond the headlines of the newspapers,"},{"time":891000,"text":"including the personal relationship that you have"},{"time":893000,"text":"with friends and family."},{"time":896000,"text":"You got to question everything that is told to you,"},{"time":899000,"text":"including what I just told you today."},{"time":901000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":903000,"text":"This is the only way for you"},{"time":905000,"text":"to step into the dark side, and have a look at it."},{"time":908000,"text":"And believe me,"},{"time":910000,"text":"it's going to be scary."},{"time":912000,"text":"It's going to be frightful, but it's going to enlighten you."},{"time":915000,"text":"And, above all, it's not going to be boring."},{"time":918000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":920000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}